title: Pancakeswap fan token
body:
Create pancakeswap fan token, and sell it and the money use to buy back and burn cake

the usage of the token is to increase the max staked for new coin launch at syrup pool, for eg 1 fan token can increase the max staked to 200 cake or more. To able to stake 200cake, first must stake 1 fan token. 

After used the fan token burn it.
author: 0xcE18116dA1a4A0282B0093f4969576949c60Be57
